|3 |    ├─PX BLOCK ITERATOR                 |        |
|4 |    │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN                 |t1      |
|5 |    └─MATERIAL                          |        |
|6 |      └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR               |        |
|7 |        └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (BROADCAST)|:EX10000|
|8 |          └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR           |        |
|9 |            └─TABLE FULL SCAN           |t2      |
======================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
